        LINUX X64 ONLY

        Orborun is a 3D action skill run & roll game!

        Control your Orbot to collect the goods, avoid the obstacles and
        escape the hazardous Orbo-world. Complete levels on perfect run to
        unlock bonus levels. Try to reach puzzle world for a brain-teasers
        and if you will master the Orborun - twisted hazard world will be
        your final test!

        FEATURES

        - Fast, paced and fun
        - Rediscover the rolling ball games genre
        - 90+ various and rich levels in 3 robotic environments
        - 3 different robots with 27 cool Orbots skins to unlock
